biography: James Warren is from London and before becoming and actor and filmmaker represented Great Britain in Judo for twelve years winning a Gold medal at the 2002 Commonwealth Games. Warren has appeared in five Guy Ritchie films, worked with Oscar winning Director Guiseppe Tornatore (Cinema Paradiso) and most recently Tom Paton playing the role of Bartlett in the upcoming 400 Bullets.
name: James Warren
